    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>cornflour </strong>and<strong> remaining soy sauce </strong>in the reserved bowl<strong> </strong>with your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat go easy!), <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>,<strong> tahini </strong>and<strong> rice vinegar</strong></p><p>Add 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[65ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[80ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>– this is your<strong> dan dan-style sauce</strong></p>",
