      "instruction": "<p>When the tofu is nearly ready, add your <strong>udon noodles</strong> to a bowl and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Set aside to soak for 1-2 min, then stir to separate the noodles</p><p>Drain the <strong>soaked noodles</strong></p>",
